{"tid":56463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"津巴布韋用動物償還中國債務","createTime":"2016-12-27T09:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T03:38:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db1332b9ce65ee915bf34746c326381e3437fee0","tid":56463,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:08:43.000Z","msg":"<strong>辛巴威用小象　償還中國債務</strong><br />\n2016/12/27 06:34 <br />\n<br />\n非洲國家辛巴威的動保人士向英國《泰晤士報》踢爆，辛巴威總統總統穆加比（Robert Mugabe）的51歲妻子格雷絲（Grace Mugabe）<strong>把35頭小象、8隻獅子、12隻土狼及1隻長頸鹿送給中國一處動物園，用來償還欠下的軍服債務。</strong><br />\n<br />\n辛巴威因購買用軍服和軍靴而欠債，據報這批動物經俄羅斯莫斯科空運到中國上海，再轉送到廣州的長隆野生動物世界。報導估計，一頭大象值4萬至6萬美元（約128.82萬至193.23萬台幣）。<br />\n<br />\n辛巴威的野生動物事務官員為生擒野生小象辯護，聲稱此舉可為國內野生動物公園減輕「過重」的負擔。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161227/640_30df573dec95e615a8deb1180387b6a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161227%2F640_30df573dec95e615a8deb1180387b6a2.jpg&h=9ead571e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝《印度時報》<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161227/1021450\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20161227%2F1021450&d=gf5Gdp6S7239pWTH0YeD2WN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=f1b06a28\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20161227/1021450</a>"},{"pid":"82d64dc5cfa287c1b368261b3fa3e2ae6b28085b","tid":56463,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都得？"},{"pid":"eb1a3072d0c1ccf71c0ff0ade9e8d526cd95cea6","tid":56463,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:13:34.000Z","msg":"中國盟友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32a29d429d41c777666c995a9b88775dbaa6a33","tid":56463,"uid":6222,"like":0,"d